                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#3r">Fol. 3r</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 3r: ዝመጽሓፍ፡ ዘአባ፡ ገብረ፡ ሕይወት፡ ዘወሀባ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ምሕረት፡ ማየ፡ አንበሳ፡ ድብር፡ ገነት፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note states that Gäbrä Ḥǝywät donated the Ms. to the monastery of May ʾAnbäsa.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#58vb">Fols. 58vb-59</locus>r: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fols. 58vb: ዝመጽሓፍ፡ ዘአባ፡ ገብረ፡ ሕይወት፡ ዘአጥረዩ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፨ በ፲፻፳፫ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፨ ወወሀባ፡ ለኪዳነ፡ ምሕረት፡ ማየ፡ አንበሳ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፨</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note states that Gäbrä Ḥǝywät bought the Ms. with his money and donated it to the monastery of May ʾAnbäsa in the year 1930/31 A.D. (the date is misspelled, but can be resonctructed to the year of mercy 1923 = 1930/31 A.D.).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ʾArdǝʾǝt has been written in blue paint on the front board.</item>
                     </list>
